DALLAS JOINT STOCK LAND BANK OF DALLAS, Appellant, v. Israel Henry SPIKES, Bankrupt, Appellee. No. 8185. Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. May 18, 1937.

Before FOSTER, SIBLEY, and HOLMES, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The petition for rehearing in the above numbered and entitled cause is denied.
